FEATURED PRODUCT OF THE WEEK

Discussing Your Development Plan Video
Two new skills model videos will add important content and process
to your mentoring orientations.
"Discussing Your Development Plan" models a protege involving both
her mentor and manager in developing her action plan. In less than
six minutes, this video shows the key steps in this important discussion.
"Negotiating Your Mentoring Agreement" is the foundation for a successful
mentoring experience. You will see a protégé and mentor negotiate the
critical points in a mentoring agreement

http://www.hr.com/hrcom/clickthru/clickthru.cfm?linkid=1012801003

